msgid ""
"For now, we only calculated city-wide CO₂-Budgets for the German cities "
"Berlin, Bonn, Hamburg, Heidelberg and Karlsruhe. City-wide CO₂-Budgets are "
"relevant to limit global warming to certain temperatures. If you are "
"interested, we can evaluate if a calculation for your city is possible."
